"reflections for small details."
msgstr ""
"透過將反射探頭與螢幕空間反射相結合，您可以兩全其美：一般房間結構的高品質反射"
"（在螢幕外時仍然存在），同時還可以對小細節進行即時反射。"

msgid "Reflections in a room using ReflectionProbe only."
msgstr "僅使用 ReflectionProbe 在房間中進行反射。"

msgid ""
"Reflections in a room using ReflectionProbe only. Notice how small details "
"don't have any reflections."
msgstr "僅使用 ReflectionProbe 在房間中進行反射。請注意，小細節沒有任何反射。"

msgid "Reflections in a room using screen-space reflections only."
msgstr "僅使用螢幕空間反射在房間中進行反射。"

msgid ""
"Reflections in a room using screen-space reflections only. Notice how the "
"reflection on the sides of the room's walls is partly missing due to being "
"off-screen."
msgstr ""
"僅使用螢幕空間反射在房間中進行反射。請注意，房間牆壁側面的反射由於不在螢幕上"
"而部分遺失。"

msgid ""
"Reflections in a room using ReflectionProbe and screen-space reflections "
"together."
msgstr "房間中的反射同時使用 ReflectionProbe 和螢幕空間反射。"

